            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1265104274,
            "creation_date": 1265103183,
            "body": "<p>You'd better go with a composite primary key.<\/p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://weblogs.java.net/blog/2006/11/29/using-composite-keys-jpa\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">This article<\/a> explains how to do it with JPA annotations. It uses <code>@Embeddable<\/code> and <code>@EmbeddedId<\/code><\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 2182991,
            "question_id": 2182950,
            "last_edit_date": 1265104274
        }
